𝑻𝒂𝒓𝒂, 𝒔𝒂𝒎𝒂𝒉𝒂𝒏 𝒎𝒐𝒏𝒈 𝒍𝒖𝒎𝒊𝒑𝒂𝒅 𝒂𝒏𝒈 𝒅𝒆𝒑𝒂𝒓𝒕𝒎𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒏𝒂 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒇𝒆𝒄𝒕 𝒔𝒂'𝒚𝒐! 🎈

Parang hot air balloon sa Pampanga, sabay-sabay nating iangat ang leadership, talent, at campus fun ng bawat Tamaraw! 🌟

Sa FEU College Y Club, marami kang pwedeng salihan! 😎✨

Kaya ano pang hinihintay mo?🫵🏻 Let’s make this academic year full of fun, learning, and unforgettable experiences! 💛

Apply na! 💌
https://bit.ly/CYCApplication2526

#DefyingLimits

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We celebrate not only your special day but also the dedication, and talent you bring our dear 𝐌𝐬. 𝐊𝐲𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐍𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐋𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬.

The ITHM Student Council sends you our warmest greetings—cheers to you, and to another year of success and growth! 

May this year bring you more a greater opportunities, and endless moments of happiness. Continue to shine and lead with the same enthusiasm that uplifts everyone around you. ✨🩷

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

We celebrate not only your special day but also the dedication, and talent you bring our dear 𝐌𝐬. 𝐊𝐲𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐍𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐋𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬.

The ITHM Student Council sends you our warmest greetings—cheers to you, and to another year of success and growth! 

May this year bring you more a greater opportunities, and endless moments of happiness. Continue to shine and lead with the same enthusiasm that uplifts everyone around you. ✨🩷

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

We celebrate not only your special day but also the dedication, and talent you bring our dear 𝐌𝐬. 𝐊𝐲𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐍𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐋𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬.

The ITHM Student Council sends you our warmest greetings—cheers to you, and to another year of success and growth! 

May this year bring you more a greater opportunities, and endless moments of happiness. Continue to shine and lead with the same enthusiasm that uplifts everyone around you. ✨🩷

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We celebrate not only your special day but also the dedication, and talent you bring our dear 𝐌𝐬. 𝐊𝐲𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐍𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐋𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬.

The ITHM Student Council sends you our warmest greetings—cheers to you, and to another year of success and growth! 

May this year bring you more a greater opportunities, and endless moments of happiness. Continue to shine and lead with the same enthusiasm that uplifts everyone around you. ✨🩷

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We celebrate not only your special day but also the dedication, and talent you bring our dear 𝐌𝐬. 𝐊𝐲𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞 𝐍𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐋𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬.

The ITHM Student Council sends you our warmest greetings—cheers to you, and to another year of success and growth! 

May this year bring you more a greater opportunities, and endless moments of happiness. Continue to shine and lead with the same enthusiasm that uplifts everyone around you. ✨🩷

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
